<statement>
<p>What are the solutions to <m>\displaystyle{5}{\left({x}+{2}\right)}^{{2}}-{15}={0}</m>? <fillin characters="12" /></p>
<p>Round solutions to two decimal places.</p>

</statement>
<solution>
<p><ul><li>-0.27,-3.73</li></ul></p><p><m>\displaystyle{5}{\left({x}+{2}\right)}^{{2}}-{15}={0}</m></p>
<p><m>\displaystyle{5}{\left({x}+{2}\right)}^{{2}}={15}</m></p>
<p><m>\displaystyle{\left({x}+{2}\right)}^{{2}}={3}</m></p>
<p><m>\displaystyle{x}+{2}=\pm{1.7320508075689}</m></p>
<p><m>\displaystyle{x}=-{2}\pm{1.7320508075689}</m></p>
<p><m>\displaystyle{x}=-{0.26794919243112},-{3.7320508075689}</m></p>
<p><m>\displaystyle{x}=-{0.27},-{3.73}</m></p>
</solution>
</myopenmath>

